breakingChangesNotes:
• Removed `close_reasons` from integration parameter list
  • Removed commands: `arcanna-get-feedback-field`, `arcanna-get-default-job-id`, `arcanna-set-default-job-id`, `arcanna-send-bulk-events`

  • Parameters changed for command `arcanna-send-event-feedback`

    • Removed parameter `close_reason` and `label` with parameter `feedback` - should contain the decision to be sent to Arcanna.ai for a specific incident ( see command *arcanna-get-decision-set* for reference )
    • Removed parameter `closing_notes` - Have only the feedback sent at this playbook step, closing notes not used anymore in Arcanna.ai
    • Removed parameter `indicators` - Have only the feedback sent at this playbook step, indicators not used anymore in Arcanna.ai
    • Added parameter `decision_set` - Used to validate that provided feedback is valid for specified AI Job ( values used from *arcanna-get-decision-set* )
